title: Lana Del Rey - Young & Beautiful (D-Boyz Remix).mp3
description:
Well, we present to you our first Remix on the song "Young & Beautiful" by Lana Del Rey. Hope you enjoy it.

Video edit was made by one of our member's brother.

D-Boyz is a new team with one DJ and one Producer from Greece. The variety of their music is about RnB & House Remixes and Mashups. Our beginning was set this summer because we need to give you the chance to listen to our songs, enjoy, critisize us so you can work harder to improve our abilities on music.
Periodically we will upload our remixes and mashups with differents songs from a big variety of artists from RnB & House stage.
